## 🚫 STRICT CONSTRAINTS (NEVER BREAK)

### **CSS Hard Rules**

- **❌ NO AUTO-CREATE VARIABLES** — Use only existing variables from `variables.css`
- **❌ NO INLINE STYLES** — Use CSS classes only
- **❌ NO DISPLAY: GRID** — Use `display: flex; flex-direction: column;` instead
- **❌ NO MAGIC NUMBERS** — Use CSS variables and named constants
- **⚠️ HARD-CODED VALUES EXCEPTIONS** — Only for truly unique cases:

#### **🚫 GRID-MOD VIOLATIONS (NEVER BREAK)**

- **❌ NO CSS DECLARATIONS FOR GRID-MOD ELEMENTS** — If element uses `grid="..."` attribute, DO NOT declare:
  - `display: grid`, `display: flex`, `flex-direction`
  - `grid-template-columns`, `grid-template-rows`
  - `gap`, `grid-gap`
  - Any responsive `@media` rules for layout
- **✅ GRID-MOD HANDLES AUTOMATICALLY**:
  - Layout structure (display, grid, flex)
  - Responsive breakpoints
  - Gap spacing
  - Column calculations
- **✅ ALLOWED CSS FOR GRID-MOD ELEMENTS**:
  - Component-specific styles (colors, borders, shadows)
  - Typography (font-size, font-weight)
  - Transforms and animations
  - Padding and margins (not layout-related)

#### **Allowed Hard-coded Values**

- **Single elements without siblings** (hamburger menu lines, icon parts, borders)
- **Specific design requirements** where no suitable variable exists
- **Performance critical** elements where direct values are optimal
- **Special positioning** effects (negative margins, complex transforms)
- **Micro-interactions** that require precise pixel values
- **SVG viewBox** and icon dimensions
- **Complex calculations** where direct values are clearer than calc()

#### **Examples of Allowed Hard-coding**

````css
.hamburger-line {
  height: 2px; /* Unique menu line thickness */
}

.icon-part {
  width: 1px; /* Specific icon detail */
}

.micro-animation {
  transform: translateY(-3px); /* Precise hover effect */
}

.special-border {
  border: 1px solid #f0f0f0; /* Very specific border */
}
```

### **Animation Performance**

- **✅ ALLOWED**: `transform` and `opacity` only (60fps)
- **❌ FORBIDDEN**: `width`, `height`, `left`, `top`, `margin`, `padding`

### **Variable Violations**

- **❌ NEVER**: `--color-border`, `--color-background`, `--color-text`, `--color-text-muted`, `--color-primary`
- **✅ ALWAYS**: `--main-color-8`, `--color-white`, `--main-color-2`, `--main-color-6`, `--main-color-1`

