## 🎨 GRID-MOD SYSTEM RULES

### **When to Use Grid-Mod**

- **✅ USE**: Components with 3+ items requiring complex responsive behavior
- **❌ SKIP**: Hero, CTA, Header, Footer, simple 2-column layouts

### **Grid-Mod Patterns**

```html
<!-- Features: 6→3→2→1 columns -->
<div grid="6,3,2,1,var(--gap-md)">...</div>

<!-- Testimonials: 4→2→1→1 columns -->
<div grid="4,2,1,1,var(--gap-lg)">...</div>

<!-- Pricing: 3→2→1→1 columns -->
<div grid="3,2,1,1,var(--gap-xl)">...</div>
```

### **Breakpoint Mapping**

- **Small**: ≤480px (mobile)
- **Semi**: ≤992px (tablet)
- **Medium**: ≤1200px (desktop)
- **Large**: >1200px (wide)

